quran[7]{c,v,t,f}:
  76,6,"This will be a gushing spring wherefrom Allah's servants shall drink wine, a spring from which they will take out channels wherever they wish."{1}{2}{3},footnotes:1:1,footnotes:2:2,footnotes:3:3
  76,7,"These will be the ones who fulfil their vows and dread the Day whose woe shall be spread far and wide;"{1},footnotes:1:1
  76,8,"those who, for the love of Him, feed the needy, and the orphan, and the captive,"{1}{2},footnotes:1:1,footnotes:2:2
  76,9,"(saying): “We feed you only for Allah's sake; we do not seek of you any recompense or thanks,"{1}{2},footnotes:1:1,footnotes:2:2
  76,10,"we fear from our Lord a Day that shall be long and distressful.”"